---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About MoltyFlywheel" description="The story behind the AI Affiliate Flywheel and how we use OpenClaw to automate affiliate marketing.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8">About MoltyFlywheel</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-amber max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">MoltyFlywheel is more than just an affiliate site — it's a live laboratory for AI-driven marketing automation.</p>
      <p>Built on the <strong>OpenClaw</strong> framework, we use a library of 52 specialized AI skills to research niches, identify high-converting affiliate programs, and generate high-quality content that ranks.</p>
      <h2>Our Philosophy: The Flywheel Effect</h2>
      <p>In the world of AI marketing, speed and scale are your greatest assets. The MoltyFlywheel system is designed to create a self-reinforcing cycle:</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>AI Skills</strong> generate optimized content daily.</li>
        <li><strong>Search Engines</strong> index and rank this content for target keywords.</li>
        <li><strong>Traffic</strong> converts into affiliate revenue.</li>
        <li><strong>Revenue</strong> is reinvested into more advanced AI skills and scaling.</li>
      </ol>
      <p>We share our findings, tools, and strategies openly so you can build your own flywheel.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
